1
00:01:04,680 --> 00:01:06,440
How about this?

2
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:08,440
Drink.

3
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:11,960
General, Empress Dowager wants to see you.

4
00:01:13,600 --> 00:01:15,039
Let her in.

5
00:01:15,039 --> 00:01:15,920
Yes.

6
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:28,440
I seem to have disturbed you.

7
00:01:36,240 --> 00:01:37,800
I've long heard that you're brave.

8
00:01:38,759 --> 00:01:39,960
I saw it with my own eyes.

9
00:01:41,320 --> 00:01:43,759
General, that's nothing.

10
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:26,160
I'm waiting for you.

11
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:29,000
Show me.

12
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:31,000
Your trump card

13
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:33,680
is not for you to fall in love.

14
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,360
What?

15
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:40,640
You don't like it?

16
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:48,880
Your tricks

17
00:02:50,440 --> 00:02:52,000
I'm exactly what I want.

18
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:55,840
Be careful, General.

19
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:59,600
Falling in love with someone who doesn't like you

20
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,240
is dangerous.

21
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:23,920
You worry too much.

22
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:26,320
That's not what I meant.

23
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:28,960
Is it good?

24
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:12,120
I got the tally.

25
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,520
but we haven't found the antidote.

26
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:15,880
Find it while you have time.

27
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:17,760
Did you kiss him?

28
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:19,800
I asked you to lure him

29
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:21,440
to put the medicine in the wine

30
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:22,400
and lure him to drink it.

31
00:04:23,080 --> 00:04:24,280
I didn't ask you to kiss him.

32
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:26,720
What does it have to do with you?

33
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,640
You...

34
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:30,280
General, Lieutenant General Wu wants to see you.

35
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:31,240
General.

36
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:32,480
General.

37
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:34,240
General!

38
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:39,400
Oh no, there's an assassin!

39
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:40,680
Call the military doctor.

40
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:41,840
Others search.

41
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:43,760
This way.

42
00:04:43,760 --> 00:04:44,560
General.

43
00:04:45,440 --> 00:04:46,240
General!

44
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:47,600
General.

45
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:54,600
Search carefully.

46
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,600
Is there anyone over there?

47
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:06,280
Let's go over there.

48
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,120
Hurry.

49
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,520
Search carefully.

50
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:15,320
If you don't use invisibility,

51
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:18,280
we'll be caught red-handed.

52
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:35,120
General.

53
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,200
General.

54
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:40,800
The Empress Dowager is missing.

55
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:41,880
What?

56
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,200
Go after him!

57
00:05:43,640 --> 00:05:44,480
Go after them!

58
00:05:52,440 --> 00:05:54,120
They've left, right?

59
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:56,880
I can take you out of here.

60
00:05:56,960 --> 00:05:59,280
Why were you hiding here?

61
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,040
General, no one is here.

62
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:46,600
General.

63
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,520
No.

64
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,040
General.

65
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,000
Not here either.

66
00:06:50,159 --> 00:06:52,920
The Demon Queen must have planned this.

67
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:56,040
Oh no.

68
00:06:56,760 --> 00:07:00,400
I must have sneaked into the Camp.

69
00:07:00,960 --> 00:07:01,800
Pass my order.

70
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:03,240
Forbid the city.

71
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:04,440
You can only enter or leave.

72
00:07:04,760 --> 00:07:05,760
Yes.

73
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:28,600
You're right.

74
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,720
After the new emperor ascended the throne,

75
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:32,360
he killed all the palace maids and eunuchs

76
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:34,240
who served the late emperor.

77
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:36,080
I saved a little eunuch

78
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:38,520
and learned that the death of the late emperor wasn't an accident.

79
00:07:38,520 --> 00:07:39,320
It was the new emperor.

80
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,600
Ji Hong Zhen

81
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:44,640
is just an arrogant fool.

82
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,680
Those royal relatives

83
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:47,720
and aristocrats.

84
00:07:48,280 --> 00:07:50,440
can never submit to him.

85
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:54,120
Let the people in the capital move.

86
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:57,159
and spread the news about me in Baili Jinghong.

87
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:59,000
Tell them

88
00:07:59,320 --> 00:08:03,120
General Baili ignored the royal power and kidnapped Empress Dowager.

89
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:05,120
He must be disloyal.

90
00:08:14,520 --> 00:08:16,200
No matter

91
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,600
or not,

92
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:20,800
I will force him to rebel.

93
00:08:21,280 --> 00:08:23,120
He made it. I got the royal power.

94
00:08:23,520 --> 00:08:25,000
He failed.

95
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,240
I have military power.

96
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:28,720
When the crickets fight, the fisherman wins.

97
00:08:29,400 --> 00:08:30,800
I have to

98
00:08:31,760 --> 00:08:33,120
I have to take one.

99
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:14,160
I didn't see you drink too much before.

100
00:09:15,160 --> 00:09:15,960
It's cold.

101
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,320
It's just warm up.

102
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:34,200
Your Highness drank too fast.

103
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,240
It's bad for your health.

104
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,680
It's cold and warm up.

105
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,840
You chose a good yard.

106
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:38,840
Young Master.

107
00:10:41,040 --> 00:10:42,120
Where am I?

108
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:44,000
The residence that Empress Dowager asked Huo Ling Yu to find.

109
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:45,560
General Shen was also rescued.

110
00:10:45,560 --> 00:10:46,960
and placed here.

111
00:10:49,040 --> 00:10:50,840
It's such a meticulous arrangement.

112
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:51,840
I think

113
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:54,480
her men in the Camp must have followed us.

114
00:10:55,680 --> 00:10:56,680
The tally is lost.

115
00:10:57,040 --> 00:10:58,840
General is looking for you.

116
00:10:58,840 --> 00:10:59,600
Bai...

117
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:01,080
Are you picking a fight?

118
00:11:10,160 --> 00:11:11,400
You're awake.

119
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:13,600
What’s your plan?

120
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:15,720
I'll go back and find the antidote.

121
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:17,880
It looks safe here.

122
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:19,640
Wait for me here.

123
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:22,000
Whether I can find it or not,

124
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,640
I will come here

125
00:11:23,640 --> 00:11:24,880
to meet you.

126
00:11:37,560 --> 00:11:38,840
It's getting cold.

127
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:40,320
This is a warm jade from volcano.

128
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:44,360
It's good for your health.

129
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:54,280
Three days.

130
00:11:55,520 --> 00:11:56,720
I'll give you three days at most.

131
00:11:57,400 --> 00:11:58,200
Okay.

132
00:12:16,800 --> 00:12:18,200
Shen Mingyue, let me tell you.

133
00:12:18,400 --> 00:12:19,480
In this world,

134
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:21,520
no one loves you more than I do.

135
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:22,640
What I said just now

136
00:12:22,880 --> 00:12:23,680
are sincere.

137
00:12:24,640 --> 00:12:25,560
Mother, you're wrong.

138
00:12:25,560 --> 00:12:26,520
She's not a loser.

139
00:12:27,400 --> 00:12:28,720
She is the light in my heart.

140
00:12:29,880 --> 00:12:31,160
glib-tongued.

141
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:33,360
I don't know

142
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:35,240
if it’s true.

143
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:51,000
I’ve been in the north for years.

144
00:12:52,040 --> 00:12:53,680
If I want to control the North,

145
00:12:53,920 --> 00:12:55,640
the commander's seal is not enough.

146
00:12:57,280 --> 00:12:58,360
If I kill him,

147
00:12:58,960 --> 00:13:01,960
I don't have a powerful general to be used by me.

148
00:13:02,280 --> 00:13:04,480
The North will cause chaos.

149
00:13:05,680 --> 00:13:06,680
He Lian Jin.

150
00:13:07,560 --> 00:13:09,360
Will you let me down?

151
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:44,320
Aoyi's medicine doesn't work anymore.

152
00:13:45,520 --> 00:13:47,840
I don't know how long I can live.

153
00:13:50,640 --> 00:13:52,400
General, I'm incompetent.

154
00:13:52,400 --> 00:13:53,480
I couldn't find the Empress Dowager.

155
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:57,760
Shen Lian and Huo escaped.

156
00:14:10,840 --> 00:14:11,760
Tell me.

157
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:13,600
Where did they go?

158
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:16,280
I...

159
00:14:17,280 --> 00:14:18,600
I don't know.

160
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:23,400
They all left.

161
00:14:24,640 --> 00:14:26,200
and left you alone.

162
00:14:27,400 --> 00:14:29,560
Are you still going to hide it for them?

163
00:14:30,920 --> 00:14:32,200
Her Highness only said

164
00:14:32,680 --> 00:14:35,800
send someone to send me out to reunite with my family.

165
00:14:37,040 --> 00:14:39,120
I really don't know anything else.

166
00:14:43,920 --> 00:14:45,240
If you don't know,

167
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:47,520
it's useless to keep it.

168
00:14:47,520 --> 00:14:48,880
Kill him.

169
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:49,920
General.

170
00:14:51,480 --> 00:14:52,480
Please spare her life.

171
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:55,320
I'm willing to take 100 batons

172
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:56,480
for her life.

173
00:15:00,080 --> 00:15:03,040
General, she is just a maid.

174
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:05,880
I won't tell her the details of the Empress Dowager's escape.

175
00:15:05,920 --> 00:15:07,280
Please show mercy.

176
00:15:09,400 --> 00:15:10,120
Come on.

177
00:15:10,640 --> 00:15:12,320
You're useless.

178
00:15:16,560 --> 00:15:18,040
Thank you, General.

179
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:47,280
You're mine now.

180
00:15:48,520 --> 00:15:52,000
General, I won't hurt you again.

181
00:15:52,320 --> 00:15:53,520
Don't be afraid.

182
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:55,680
Why did you save me?

183
00:15:59,720 --> 00:16:00,960
I like you.

184
00:16:02,040 --> 00:16:02,840
I...

185
00:16:04,040 --> 00:16:05,440
I won't like you.

186
00:17:07,280 --> 00:17:07,760
Jiaga.
